Class ListItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devtence.will.dev.models.ListItem

  • public class ListItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper Class for basic listing functionality for Endpoints, this class also provides an easy way to access the total amount of elements generated by the query for pagination purposes and the cursor index generated by the Google Cloud Datastore.

    2015-10-12
